        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_Published_AccountAndMeterListing_Upgrade",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve and log information about accounts and meters associated with a specific agency and facility. It determines the published billing period based on whether the user is an agency user or not, logs the report usage, and then retrieves account and meter details from a view, filtering based on the provided agency code and facility number."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
