        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves conditional logic, dynamic data retrieval, and joins with user-defined table functions, which adds to its complexity. The use of multiple parameters and conditional branching increases the complexity beyond a simple query execution."
        }
      ]
    },
